<ns10:section xmlns:ns10="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.concepts.architecture.referenceArchitectures.introduction.disadvantages">

  <ns11:title xmlns:ns11="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Disadvantages of using reference architectures</ns11:title>
  <ns12:para xmlns:ns12="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
    he disadvantage of being too focused on using reference architectures is that your organization
    is less likely to come up with novel solutions which could have provided a competitive edge.
  </ns12:para>
